## This is the hook collection for git used by polyvi daily development.

## Every hook should be in a separate dir, with source and a readme file.

## How to install hooks?
1. clone this repo at a fixed location
2. cd into your project repo
3. run command at the root of your project repo
    ln -s path/to/hooks-repo/pre-commit/pre-commit.sh .git/hooks/pre-commit
4. now installation done

## For Windows users, you should have a bash or bash compatible environment
